These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, tea, water, juice
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, hedgehog, guinea-pig, horse
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, helicopter, car, trike
1. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the person drinking juice is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is the owner of the goldfish##1
5. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
6. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
7. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage    | tea  | juice | water    | lemonade       |
| Pet         | hedgehog | horse    | guinea-pig      | goldfish |
| Transport   | taxi   | car | helicopter | trike        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-2::.
There 4 different types of food: subwayrot, cherry, lettuce, potato
The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, bartender, doctor, accountant
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, subway, airplane, jet-ski
1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the accountant##1
2. the person eating potato is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
3. the doctor is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
4. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
5. the person driving the taxi is the firefighter##1
6. the person driving the jet-ski is the person eating cherry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |       3       |     4     |
| Food        | lettuce   | cherry | subwayrot     | potato      |
| Job         | bartender | doctor | accountant | firefighter |
| Transport   | subway    | jet-ski   | airplane     | taxi      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, card-games, collecting, board-games
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, salsa, techno, gospel
There are 4 different nationalities: german, italian, turkish, pakistani
1. the fan of salsa is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the italian is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
3. the fan of gospel is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is the fan of techno##1
5. the pakistani is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
6. the pakistani is on the right of the turkish##1
7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the german##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | woodworking | card-games | collecting | board-games |
| Music-Genre   | gospel       | salsa    | house | techno     |
| Nationality   | german | turkish    | pakistani | italian    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, journalist, accountant, police-officer
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, weightlifting, skiing, surfing
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, bike, snowmobile, roller
1. the accountant is the person driving the roller##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
4. the journalist is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is climbing is the accountant##1
7. the accountant is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
8. the police-officer is on the right of the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |        2        |     3      |      4      |
| Job         | scientist | police-officer | accountant | journalist |
| Sport       | weightlifting     | surfing      | climbing     | skiing      |
| Transport   | bike | scooter         | roller      | snowmobile        |

