.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, woodworking, fishing, reading
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, disaster, sports, family
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, rugby, cricket, swimming
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
4. the person who's sport is sailing is the person watching sports movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person watching disaster movies##1
7. the person who's hobby is reading is the person who's sport is cricket##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | fishing   | reading | woodworking  | filmmaking      |
| Movie-Genre   | sports  | action        | family  | disaster       |
| Sport         | sailing | cricket    | rugby | swimming |

