.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  videographer, teacher, bartender, pilot
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, scientific, western, spy
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, punk, jazz, salsa
1. the videographer is the fan of punk##1
2. the fan of house is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
3. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the pilot##1
4. the fan of salsa is on the far left##1
5. the teacher is on the far left##1
6. the person watching western movies is the bartender##1
7. the fan of punk is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
8. the pilot is the fan of jazz##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | teacher | bartender | pilot | videographer |
| Movie-Genre   | spy   | western  | scientific | epic   |
| Music-Genre   | salsa   | house     | jazz | punk       |

