.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-7::.
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, carrot, lettuce, eggplant
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, filmmaking, board-games, rock-climbing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, animation, crime, scientific
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far right##1
2. the person eating carrot is on the far right##1
3. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
4. the person watching animation movies is the person eating lettuce##1
5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
6. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
7. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
8. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Food          | pumpkin  | eggplant | lettuce   | carrot     |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | filmmaking   | sudoku  | board-games |
| Movie-Genre   | crime         | epic  | animation | scientific  |

