.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, lemonade, milk, fanta
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, western, superhero, zombie
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, indonesian, australian, malaysian
1. the person drinking lemonade is the australian##1
2. the malaysian is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
3. the person watching western movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the australian##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
6. the malaysian is the person drinking milk##1
7. the indonesian is on the left of the malaysian##1
8. the person drinking lemonade is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | fanta | milk     | cola | lemonade |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie  | satire | superhero       | western    |
| Nationality   | indonesian   | malaysian | egyptian    | australian |

