.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-9::.
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, kale, radish, eggplant
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, electronic, house, techno
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, biathlon, parkour, handball
1. the fan of electronic is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
3. the fan of electronic is on the left of the fan of house##1
4. the person who's sport is parkour is the person eating kale##1
5. the person eating kale is on the right of the fan of techno##1
6. the fan of techno is on the right of the person eating radish##1
7. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | radish        | eggplant   | kale  | blueberry   |
| Music-Genre   | gospel         | techno     | electronic    | house       |
| Sport         | biathlon | cricket | parkour | handball |

