.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, milk, cola, hot-chocolate
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, strawberry, apricot, avocado
4 different pets are kept: hamster, goldfish, snake, ferret
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the owner of the ferret##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
3. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
4. the person drinking juice is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
5. the person eating apricot is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking cola is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
7. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | milk    | cola | hot-chocolate | juice        |
| Food       | avocado | cauliflower  | strawberry | apricot     |
| Pet        | goldfish    | snake   | ferret  | hamster |

