.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-11::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, nurse, electrician, dressmaker
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, basketball, baseball, soccer
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, ship, roller, trike
1. the person driving the boat is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the nurse##1
3. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
4. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
5. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
6. the person driving the boat is on the left of the dressmaker##1
7. the person who's sport is surfing is the person driving the roller##1
8. the person who's sport is baseball is the police-officer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2       |       3       |       4       |
| Job         | police-officer  | dressmaker | nurse  | electrician |
| Sport       | baseball | basketball        | soccer | surfing       |
| Transport   | boat   | ship          | trike          | roller       |

