.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, woodworking, rock-climbing, gardening
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, martial-arts, thriller, spy
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, colombian, egyptian, mexican
1. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
2. the person watching spy movies is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
3. the mexican is on the left of the malaysian##1
4. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
6. the person who's hobby is photography is the egyptian##1
7. the mexican is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | gardening   | rock-climbing   | photography | woodworking |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | drama | martial-arts   | spy |
| Nationality   | mexican     | malaysian  | egyptian  | colombian  |

