.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-13::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, sudoku, singing, filmmaking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, electronic, d&b, hip-hop
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, surfing, cricket, weightlifting
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is the fan of hip-hop##1
3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
6. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
7. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4    |
| Hobby         | filmmaking | sudoku    | collecting        | singing |
| Music-Genre   | electronic     | d&b     | hip-hop        | salsa   |
| Sport         | surfing   | golf | cricket | weightlifting  |

