.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-14::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, horror, spy, thriller
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, argentine, indian, dutch
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, trike, snowmobile, tram
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the indian##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the right of the dutch##1
3. the mexican is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
4. the person driving the tram is on the left of the indian##1
5. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
6. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
7. the person watching spy movies is on the far right##1
8. the argentine is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | horror   | thriller  | zombie    | spy    |
| Nationality   | dutch | indian  | mexican  | argentine |
| Transport     | tram  | trike | snowmobile | quad-bike        |

