.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-15::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, lemonade, milk, 7up
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, western, satire, drama
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, cycling, golf, badminton
1. the person who's sport is sailing is the person drinking milk##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
3. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
4. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
5. the person watching drama movies is the person drinking 7up##1
6. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
7. the person drinking juice is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
8. the person watching satire movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | juice        | 7up    | lemonade | milk      |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts        | drama   | western  | satire  |
| Sport         | badminton | cycling | golf   | sailing |

