3. the fan of disco is on the right of the american##1
4. the fan of blues is the american##1
5. the teacher is on the far left##1
6. the police-officer is on the right of the nigerian##1
7. the thai is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Job           | teacher  | analyst | designer  | police-officer |
| Music-Genre   | blues    | disco       | soul | jazz      |
| Nationality   | american | pakistani  | nigerian    | thai    |

