.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-18::.
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, pakistani, polish, german
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, parkour, snowboarding, soccer
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, bike, boat, helicopter
1. the pakistani is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
2. the person driving the bus is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the bike is on the right of the japanese##1
4. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the person driving the boat is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
7. the polish is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Nationality   | japanese | pakistani | polish | german |
| Sport         | parkour | ice-hockey | soccer  | snowboarding  |
| Transport     | bus  | bike | helicopter     | boat  |

