.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  paramedic, project-manager, manager, writer
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, polish, colombian, german
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, baseball, weightlifting, cricket
1. the project-manager is on the left of the argentine##1
2. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the manager##1
3. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far right##1
4. the colombian is on the far right##1
5. the argentine is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
6. the german is on the far left##1
7. the writer is on the far right##1
8. the german is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |       4        |
| Job           | project-manager  | manager  | paramedic | writer |
| Nationality   | german   | argentine | polish   | colombian      |
| Sport         | cycling | weightlifting    | baseball   | cricket         |

 